widgets_values: If you have Triton installed, connect this for ~20-30% speed increase and reduced peak VRAM use

fp_16_fast enables "Full FP16 Accmumulation in FP16 GEMMs" feature available in the very latest pytorch nightly, this is around 20% speed boost. 

Sageattn if you have it installed can be used for almost double inference speed at higher resolutions

Radial attention is even faster but has worst quality, it should be used along with Set Radial Attention node to control which steps/blocks it's applied on to balance quality and speed.

[https://huggingface.co/Kijai/WanVideo_comfy_fp8_scaled](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/WanVideo_comfy_fp8_scaled)

Adjust the blocks to swap based on your VRAM, this is a tradeoff between speed and memory usage.
The sampling windows are constant size,  rounded up and padded with empty if there isn't enough audio
